Summary:

Overall, reviewers thought that the Friendship Bracelet Maker was easy to use and helped speed up the process of making bracelets. Some reviewers found it too complicated for younger children, but teenagers seemed to enjoy it. There were a few complaints about the quality of the materials, but most reviewers thought that the kit was a great value.

